Load-shedding is back, and it is affecting all of South Africa. Load-shedding has already reached as high as stage 6, and shows no signs of slowing down. In these tough times, it is important that you have measures in place that minimise the effect of load-shedding on your household or business. Thankfully, Takealot is a one-stop shop for all your load-shedding equipment needs. Takealot offers products ranging from power-banks for your smartphone, to generators which can power multiple devices and appliances at the same time. Here are some of the most popular products available on Takealot that can help you get through load-shedding. <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-332274" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Red-E-Power-Bank-640x430.png" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Red-E-Power-Bank-640x430.png 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Red-E-Power-Bank-595x400.png 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Red-E-Power-Bank-300x202.png 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Red-E-Power-Bank-768x516.png 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Red-E-Power-Bank.png 820w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-332276" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Romoss-Power-Bank-640x430.png" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Romoss-Power-Bank-640x430.png 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Romoss-Power-Bank-596x400.png 596w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Romoss-Power-Bank-300x202.png 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Romoss-Power-Bank-768x516.png 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-co